<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <!-- <link rel="stylesheet"  href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"/> -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>

    <title>EngineeringCircle-AdminLogin</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="CSS/styleSheet.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <%-include('commonHeader.ejs')%>

      <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col col-lg-8">
          <h5>
            Admin portal only use for offical purpose. do not violate the rules
            and regulation of offical policies,illegal use of highly
            confedential data of firm may fall you under legal violation,
          </h5>

          <br /><br />

          <h3>Precautions</h3>
          <ol>
            <li>Do n't use other admin member id and password .</li>
            <li>
              Do n't try to wrong password more than 3 time it may lock your id.
            </li>
            <li>Do n't use or share confedential (persnoal) data.</li>
            <li>Any lock id can only unblock from database side.</li>
          </ol>

          <br />
          <ul>
            <li>Please follow above Precautions to avoid any legal actions.</li>

            <li>All Rights Reserved to Engineering Cirle pvt ltd.....</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col col-lg-4">
          <form
            class="form-control border-dark rounded p-3 shadow adminForm"
            id="signInForm"
          >
            <h3>Admin Login</h3>

            <label for="userName" class="form-label"
              ><b>Please Enter Admin UserName</b></label
            >
            <input
              type="text"
              class="form-control"
              name="userId"
              id="userId"
              placeholder="UserName"
            />
            <label for="password" class="form-label"
              ><b>Please Enter Admin Password</b></label
            >
            <input
              type="password"
              class="form-control"
              name="pass"
              id="pass"
              placeholder="Password"
            />
            <div style="margin-top: 40px">
              <ul>
                <li>
                  Don't use wrong password more than 3 time it may lock your
                  password.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <input type="submit" value="Submit" class="btn btn-primary mx-5" />

            <button type="reset" value="Reset" class="btn btn-danger mx-5">
              Reset
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
   
    <script src="../script.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
